雷锋精神的践行者，让雷锋精神绽放更加璀璨的光芒。这揭示了（&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;）</span></p></div>", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "tags": ["$M002000000", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "$RE0000", "$M003002000", "ff8080814371757b014390f883db0453", "5136342961", "5036342749", "$RE0200", "6a74973a-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "$RE0201", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5", "44bebf7c-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "ff8080814371757b014390f883db0453", "5136342961", "6a74973a-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5", "44bebf7c-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4"], "status": "ONLINE", "is_publish": false, "id": "fb90af4c-e9a0-40a2-bbb6-5f634c927d73", "global_title": {"zh-CN": "（改编）2025年3月5日是第62个“学雷锋纪念日”。半个多世纪来，学雷锋活动在中华大地蔚然成风。榜样的力量激励更多人争当雷锋精神的践行者，让雷锋精神绽放更加璀璨的光芒。这揭示了（   ）"}, "global_description": {"zh-CN": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>（改编）2025年3月5日是第62个&ldquo;学雷锋纪念日&rdquo;。半个多世纪来，学雷锋活动在中华大地蔚然成风。榜样的力量激励更多人争当雷锋精神的践行者，让雷锋精神绽放更加璀璨的光芒。这揭示了（&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;）</span></p></div>"}, "global_keywords": {}, "global_label": {}, "custom_properties": {"sys_packing_status": "ready", "preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/fb90af4c-e9a0-40a2-bbb6-5f634c927d73@1.pkg/1772597669260/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597669912", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/fb90af4c-e9a0-40a2-bbb6-5f634c927d73@1.pkg/1772597669260/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597669912"}, "auto_fill_thumb": true, "prom_resouce_type": "questions", "qb_year": "2025", "nature": "tm_sync", "audit_teacher_ids": ["fcf6e075-c751-4d15-b874-d8a305f9b05c"], "version_source_id": "fb90af4c-e9a0-40a2-bbb6-5f634c927d73", "format": "2d64